          "depth": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "heading": "题解",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "<strong>理解题意</strong>",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "<strong>直观</strong>：<strong>在线询问问题</strong>，肯定不可能每次询问都跑一次背包，得一开始就跑一遍<strong>完全背包</strong>，背包容量上限为 $1e5$，硬币数没有限制。",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "<strong>深层</strong>： <strong>背包 + 容斥</strong>题，先拆解出限制条件。一共 4 个，也就是每次询问的硬币数限制。",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "<strong>正难则反</strong>，考虑违反这些硬币数限制，枚举 $2^4 - 1$ 种违反情况。",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "例如状态 <code>1000</code>，我们第一个硬币确保拿超过 <code>d[1]</code> 枚，也就是拿 <code>d[1] + 1</code>，这样违反状态 <code>1000</code> 的方案数就是 <code>dp[s - (d[1] + 1)]</code>。",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "把 $15$ 种违反状态的方案数都算出来，然后按<strong>奇减偶加</strong>的公式算最后的答案即可。",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "<strong>难点</strong>",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "看出本题是<strong>背包 + 容斥</strong>的题，得把 4 个限制条件找出来。",
          "depth": 2
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "heading": "代码",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "code",
          "lang": "cpp",
          "code": "ll dp[N], c[4], d[4];\nvoid solve(int CASE)\n{\n\tdp[0] = 1;\n\tfa(i, 0, 3) {\n\t\tcin >> c[i];\n\t\t// 完全背包 (装到装不下)\n\t\tfa(j, c[i], 1e5)dp[j] += dp[j - c[i]];\n\t}\n\tint n; cin >> n;\n\n\twhile (n--) {\n\t\tfa(i, 0, 3)cin >> d[i];\n\t\tint s; cin >> s;\n\t\tll ans = 0;\n      \t// 二进制枚举违反哪些限制条件\n\t\tfa(i, 1, 15) {\n\t\t\tint now = s;\n\t\t\tfa(k, 0, 3) if (i & (1 << k))\n\t\t\t\tnow -= (d[k] + 1) * c[k]; // 该位一定不满足要求\n\t\t\tif (now < 0)continue;\n\t\t\tif (popcnt(i) & 1)ans += dp[now];\n\t\t\telse ans -= dp[now];\n\t\t}\n\t\tcout << dp[s] - ans << endl;\n\t}\n\treturn;\n}",
          "depth": 1
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
